  "The total path length measured along the curved trajectory of the projectile, accounting for both horizontal and vertical distances traveled": "",
  "Range is the horizontal displacement of a projectile. On level ground, R = u²sin(2θ)/g, where u is the launch speed and θ is the launch angle.": "",
  "Which definition BEST describes the time of flight in projectile motion?": "",
