  "4 s — using s = ½gt²: 80 = ½(10)t² → t² = 16 → t = 4 s": "",
  "16 s — using t = 2s divided by g gives t = 160 divided by 10 = 16 seconds, doubling the height before dividing by gravitational acceleration": "",
  "s = ½gt²: 80 = 5t² → t² = 16 → t = 4 s.": "",
